{"tid":1323950,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［心態觀念］冇最後一戰呢回事","createTime":"2019-07-16T12:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T14:10:03.000Z","uid":31974,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"64066a7106c418694265a7b6ada451b238f68fbb","tid":1323950,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"正如我之前個post所言<br />\n所有人一定要做好長期抗爭既準備<br />\n<br />\n［長期抗爭］全民今日起做好準備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275828</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當局既人從來唔會知邊一仗係最後<br />\n只有歷史望返轉頭先會知道<br />\n<br />\n你攰既 就退<br />\n唔好再自殺要我地其他人行埋你個份<br />\n你想一死以逃避一切責任 恐懼<br />\n你只係自私咁將佢地推俾其他兄弟姊妹<br />\n我地已經係一個命運共同體<br />\n你條命唔係只為你自己而活<br />\n亦係為左其他同你一樣咁辛苦既人<br />\n<br />\n雖然生於呢個艱難既時代<br />\n但我好榮幸可以同你地一齊行呢條路<br />\n引用一位巴打所講<br />\n希望有一日我地可以除低口罩相見<br />\n<br />\n香港人 共勉之"},{"pid":"7dbf8923119e4749fe0b10d14046a40d3e694a9d","tid":1323950,"uid":31974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1e22c6a65f5d3596346ccf42bc4b1a076713ff","tid":1323950,"uid":224779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0358b1fce7ea0e2da16eecc9a2d88dc1a1b02d","tid":1323950,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2cc1057a6467b723642485d704401154afdaafb9","tid":1323950,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa676f0a4b0284ad500596b0d0cc0c6319e097f","tid":1323950,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"多謝你，手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有一日我地可以